{"featured_counts": 0, "common_counts": 2, "collapsed_counts": 0, "reviewing_counts": 0, "paging": {"is_end": true, "is_start": true, "next": "https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/1197440417/root_comments?limit=20&offset=20&order=time", "previous": "https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/1197440417/root_comments?limit=20&offset=0&order=time", "totals": 2}, "data": [{"id": 927447772, "type": "comment", "url": "https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/comments/927447772", "content": "<p>竟然有士气个人赞同了，那么我就再多说几句吧！我写过两本书，都过百万字的那种，另外也是没有人看的那种，我知道自己水平差，但却从来没有感觉到自己卑微，因为我勇于把自己心里的故事写出来。</p><p>兄弟们！要了解我们的社会定位，要明白我们的力量是巨大的，我们甚至于可以把眼睛看到的不公，通过文字记录下来，让那些丑陋的人，永远的定到耻辱柱上，只要还有力气写字，我们就是不可战胜的。</p><p>当然，斗争不可能一蹴而就，因此，我们首先应该明白自己的强大在那里。</p><p>兄弟们，拿起笔，给那些贪婪者留名吧！</p>", "featured": false, "collapsed": false, "is_author": false, "is_delete": false, "created_time": 1588513044, "resource_type": "answer", "reviewing": false, "allow_like": true, "allow_delete": false, "allow_reply": true, "allow_vote": true, "can_recommend": false, "can_collapse": false, "attached_info": "ggIGCAsQARgA", "author": {"role": "author", "member": {"id": "a696a5bf6744cb6c99baba185f92a93f", "url_token": "shi-shi-ji-gua-niu", "name": "笑出牙齿", "avatar_url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-27326241a8a67899511de62f9ad38c09_r.jpg", "avatar_url_template": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-27326241a8a67899511de62f9ad38c09_{size}.jpg", "is_org": false, "type": "people", "url": "https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/a696a5bf6744cb6c99baba185f92a93f", "user_type": "people", "headline": "在泥沼里唱歌", "badge": [], "gender": 1, "is_advertiser": false}}, "vote_count": 10, "reply_to_author": null, "voting": false, "disliked": false, "censor_status": 0, "child_comment_count": 0, "child_comments": []}, {"id": 927471656, "type": "comment", "url": "https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/comments/927471656", "content": "<p>长久以来，我们写网文的，常被人瞧不起，为什么？</p><p>我曾经思考过这个问题，是不是我们过于沉浸在自己幻想的世界，而忘记了我们应该承担的社会责任了？</p><p>网文不是垃圾文学，我们，也不是乌合之众。</p><p>这一次，我们要让5.5成为这个改变的开始，要让大家都看到我们的力量，让人们从此改变对我们的观感，让所有人都知道我们正在努力改变，回归到创作者该有的社会定位中去。</p><p>兄弟们，不要过于计较得得失失，我们主要是要让人们知道我们曾经为不公而斗争过，让所有人都明白，网络文学工作者，也是可以对社会不平发出自己特有的声音的。</p><p>祖国万岁，胜利最终会是属于我们的。</p>", "featured": false, "collapsed": false, "is_author": false, "is_delete": false, "created_time": 1588514473, "resource_type": "answer", "reviewing": false, "allow_like": true, "allow_delete": false, "allow_reply": true, "allow_vote": true, "can_recommend": false, "can_collapse": false, "attached_info": "ggIGCAsQARgB", "author": {"role": "author", "member": {"id": "a696a5bf6744cb6c99baba185f92a93f", "url_token": "shi-shi-ji-gua-niu", "name": "笑出牙齿", "avatar_url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-27326241a8a67899511de62f9ad38c09_r.jpg", "avatar_url_template": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-27326241a8a67899511de62f9ad38c09_{size}.jpg", "is_org": false, "type": "people", "url": "https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/a696a5bf6744cb6c99baba185f92a93f", "user_type": "people", "headline": "在泥沼里唱歌", "badge": [], "gender": 1, "is_advertiser": false}}, "vote_count": 4, "reply_to_author": null, "voting": false, "disliked": false, "censor_status": 0, "child_comment_count": 0, "child_comments": []}]}